Exosite,is,a,cloud,based,data,platform,providing,businesses,with,a,solution,for,managing,communications,between,devices,and,users,running,calculations,and,transformations,on,data,storing,and,retrieving,data,and,processing,rules,and,sending,dispatches,Users,can,try,out,the,Exosite,platform,for,free,though,full,access,to,all,features,of,the,platform,requires,enrollment,in,a,paid,program,The,Exosite,API,gives,users,programmatic,access,to,many,of,the,data,storage,and,manipulation,features,provided,by,the,Exosite,platform,This,API,operates,over,REST,and,JSON,RPC,and,uses,the,JSON,data,format